			<description>This unit of functionality intends to provide the connection between the models of the Application Protocol 236 to the generic expression schema.<p>This allows the creation of expressions to represent dependent values associated to dependent expressions.</p>
				<example>To represent an associated price dependent on a physical characteristic of the product:<p>Price = Constant * Length</p>
					<p>Where the Length is a variable to be included in the expression.</p>
